    executiveSummary: "The tokenization market is experiencing rapid growth, with the global market expected to reach $2.5 billion by 2028. This growth is driven by the increasing interest in tokenization and its applications in the crypto space. Tokenized assets have increased by 20% in the last quarter, with security tokens accounting for 60% of these assets.",
